<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blood Management System</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Blood Management System</h1>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <% if(success_msg != ''){ %>
      <div class="alert alert-success"><%= success_msg %></div>
    <% } %>
    <% if(error_msg != ''){ %>
      <div class="alert alert-danger"><%= error_msg %></div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Save Lives With Your Blood Donation</h1>
      <p>Your blood donation can save up to three lives. Join our community of donors or request blood when needed.</p>
      <img src="http://www.gapost233.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/donate_blood.jpg" alt="Blood Donation" class="hero-image">
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/login?role=donor" class="btn">Donate Blood</a>
        <a href="/login?role=recipient" class="btn btn-secondary">Receive Blood</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Why Donate Blood?</h2>
      <p>Blood donation is essential for community health. Hospitals rely on donations to save lives during emergencies, surgeries, and for patients with chronic illnesses.</p>
      <p>Every two seconds, someone in the world needs blood. A single car accident victim can require up to 100 units of blood.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

 
  
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>